snippet.title: Eternal Quest - Trailer 3
snippet.description:
Eternal Quest is a 2D MMORPG for iOS, Android and PC in the style of classic graphics. It aims to be a 2D game that brings that nostalgia of old games, but with modern, fast and dynamic gameplay and mechanics with "action" style combat and faster.

If you like 2D MMORPG, give this game a chance, because I'm sure you'll like it :)

The game has automated event systems like Team versus Team (TvT) and BOSS. The game also has many quests, craft, vast content to grind and much more!

Ah, the game is Free and no Pay2Win! ❤️

Website: https://eternal-quest.com.br
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/eternalquestgame
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1385300/Eternal_Quest__2D_MMORPG/
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.xtreming.eternalquest
App Store (iOS): https://apps.apple.com/app/apple-store/id1556838458?pt=122747498&ct=facebook&mt=8
